				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Please don't spam the area with your  "/pet back off" key.  If you have to ask your pet more than twice in a row to back off, it may be time for your /pet get lost command.
<br />

<br />
It's really REALLY hard to see what's happening when the chat window is full of your hotkey.
<br />

<br />
Last night, for instance, just using myself as an example, I (Zambik) destroyed 3 pets during Grieg when he was on the wrong side of Grieg.  I went through more than a dozen pets during the fight.  My unbuffed/unequipped pet isn't that good, but he did add a decent amount of DPS.  I imagine that necro and bst pets do as well.<br />_________________<br />Binnen Minder
<br />
