				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My 2cp as a kinda pet class.
<br />

<br />
If you are going to use Summon Companion use /follow then /sit not /guard here as when you summon him he'll start back toward his Guard point.
<br />

<br />
Shrink your pets or ask for them to be shrunk, seems to reduce frame rates and targeting boxes.
<br />

<br />
Hug a Shaman or SK pet as they need love too! <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />Iksar Shaman 65th Scale
