				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">That's what I do.
<br />

<br />
Every time I create a new character I create three new windows:
<br />

<br />
Original Main becomes "Spam" (combat, pet, spells, etc.,..)
<br />
First new window becomes "Main" (/say, /tell, /emote /group, skill msgs)
<br />
2nd new window becomes "Guildchat" (/gu, /ooc, /shout, /autojoin xxx)
<br />
3rd new window becomes "Raidchat" (/rsay)
<br />

<br />
Then I set the faded level to 25 and position all 5 windows near the bottom of the screen and make each window 4-5 lines tall.
<br />

<br />
Three across the bottom, with each of the remaining two above the left and right windows.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.arach.com/sigs/Alyxenya_Sig3.jpg">
<br />
<b>Grysm Jadeclaw</b> 56 Primalist
<br />
<b>Xelmyrion D'Tremiere</b> 52 Heretic
<br />
<b>Windrix Willowolf</b> 52 Druid
<br />
<b>Booker Freewind</b> 50 Druid<br></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
